preference.name: AWC_ExcludeTabsFromBackgroundWorkingContext
preference.preference_description: List of secondary work area tabs to be ignored by the system while restoring structure from background working context. The tab name can be the display name of the page. This behaviour will not affect retrieval of secondary work area tabs in the saved working context.
